OL,3,CCustomers describe their 'shock and
OL,4,Cstruggle' over increase in water bills
OL,6,FA man from Littlehampton says he's
OL,7,Fgoing to struggle to make ends meet
OL,8,Fafter his water bill has more than
OL,9,Fdoubled.
OL,11,FGerry De Courcy, 78, received a letter
OL,12,Ffrom Southern Water notifying him of
OL,13,Fan increase in his monthly water bill
OL,14,Ffrom #9 a month to around #22.
OL,16,FGerry lives alone in a one-bed flat,
OL,17,Fhas a basic pension, and is already
OL,18,Ftaking steps to limit his water use.
