OL,3,CCustomers describe their 'shock and
OL,4,Cstruggle' over increase in water bills
OL,6,FHe is worried about what this means
OL,7,Ffor his future and says he has tried
OL,8,Fand failed to get through to the
OL,9,Fcompany to complain.
OL,11,FHe said: ''I'm just on a state pension
OL,12,Fand that is it, and I find that an
OL,13,Fincrease that they have indicated to
OL,14,Fme is actually ridiculous. I will
OL,15,Fstruggle.
OL,17,F"I'll be hardly surprised if they keep
OL,18,Fshelling out bills like that to all
OL,19,Fand sundry."
