OL,3,CCustomers describe their 'shock and
OL,4,Cstruggle' over increase in water bills
OL,6,FSouthern Water is increasing bills by
OL,7,Fan average of 47%. That is the highest
OL,8,Frise of any of the country's suppliers.
OL,10,FRachel and Simon Exley from Brighton
OL,11,Fsay their bill from June is going up
OL,12,Ffrom #44 to #78 a month.
OL,14,FThey are bringing up two children and
OL,15,Fsay the increase in expenditure is
OL,16,Falready having an effect.
