OL,3,CCustomers describe their 'shock and
OL,4,Cstruggle' over increase in water bills
OL,6,FRachel said: ''The kids have showers
OL,7,Fnow instead of baths because, you
OL,8,Fknow, it's just the worry of will it
OL,9,Fgo up over more next year. It's quite,
OL,10,Fquite worrying actually.
OL,12,F"The impact of saying to them that you
OL,13,Fcan't have a bath anymore, you know,
OL,14,Fbecause it's costing too much. It was
OL,15,Fjust such a shock for it to go up that
OL,16,Fmuch.''
OL,18,FSouthern Water says it needs more
OL,19,Ffunds to improve its service,
OL,20,Fincluding fixing more leaks and
OL,21,Freducing storm overflows.
